txt.en: Shakhajât is well-defended by hobgoblins, so there will be no shortage of enemies for you to face inside.
Kyrstig will want to hear how many hobgoblins you faced in Shakhajât.
'There's still plenty of work to do in Shakhajât if you're up for it! Get in there and fight those hobgoblins!'
'It's time to storm Shakhajât! Let's take out as many hobgoblins as we can on the way!'
Kyrstig has given you the difficult task of storming the hobgoblin fortress of Shakhajât and facing its defenders.
'Good fighting, [placeholder]! We surely dented their numbers. Not bad for a day's work, if I say so myself!'
'How goes the fight, [placeholder]? You took down how many? Really? Good work!'
